body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello! Thank you for reaching out to Car Deals Inc. My name is Dylan Gonzalez. May I please have your name?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Dylan, my name is Linda Long.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Linda. Before we proceed, could you please provide me with your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my phone number is five five five, two zero zero, three four five six.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Linda. Next, could you share your email address with me?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, my email address is linda.long@example.com.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for providing that information, Linda. Is there anything specific I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I have a concern regarding a recent return I made to your dealership and the process was quite disappointing.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'm sorry to hear about your experience, Linda. Let's work together to resolve this. Thank you for sharing your feedback.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you again, Linda, for your time. We will do our best to improve your experience. Have a great day!
